{"word":"ἧλος","slug":"ἧλος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἧλος</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a nail</i>: in <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b> only for ornament, <i>a nail-head</i> or <i>stud.</i> <p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>after <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b> <i>a nail</i> to fasten with, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div>"}]}